of her days behind bars.

00:43.859 --> 00:45.859
You're so courageous, Bea!

00:46.658 --> 00:49.060
I would've done the same thing!

00:50.960 --> 00:52.899
How do you feel about your sentencing, Bea?

00:53.840 --> 00:54.740
Bea!

00:55.039 --> 00:56.737
We believe in you!

