04:15.759 --> 04:16.836
Clothes.

04:18.720 --> 04:21.040
- Like to watch, do you?
- Now, Smith.

04:26.000 --> 04:28.519
That's the last time you'll
be wearing those clothes.

04:28.740 --> 04:31.838
