- Hmm.

06:32.740 --> 06:33.939
How's Franky?

06:58.920 --> 07:00.519
Enjoying, you perv?

07:00.519 --> 07:03.778
Why don't you take a picture,
mate. It lasts longer.

07:03.980 --> 07:05.278
