07:12.160 --> 07:16.180
Um, we've got... pumpkin...

07:16.180 --> 07:17.680
Chickens...

07:17.680 --> 07:19.680
Cauliflower, and...

07:19.680 --> 07:21.680
- What are they, carrots?
- Yeah, carrots.

07:21.680 --> 07:22.278
Chickens.

07:22.278 --> 07:24.278
- Chickens...
- Yeah, chickens, yeah.

07:24.278 --> 07:26.278
