09:09.340 --> 09:11.158
is either information I already know...

09:11.158 --> 09:12.557
or would've undoubtedly found out...

09:12.557 --> 09:13.418
Or was just plain...

09:13.418 --> 09:15.720
- untrue.
- And what about your end of the deal?

09:15.860 --> 09:17.778
You said you'd get rid of my competitors.

09:17.778 --> 09:18.580
And I have.

09:18.580 --> 09:20.580
Except for Queen Bea.

09:20.580 --> 09:23.700
Have you forgotten about that fat ass
elephant that just walked back in the room?

09:24.700 --> 09:26.158
Well then it would help your cause...

09:26.158 --> 09:27.440
if you could give me something on her.

09:27.440 --> 09:29.080
Yeah, and yours, too.

09:31.519 --> 09:32.278
So?

09:32.798 --> 09:34.278
So?

09:36.100 --> 09:38.418
If I hear anything, I'll let you know.

09:38.418 --> 09:40.100
But I'd watch my back, if I were you.

09:40.100 --> 09:41.480
She seems to like this power thing.

09:41.480 --> 09:44.600
- Are you playing me, Doyle?
- Hey, we're all playing each other.

09:46.538 --> 09:48.440
- We finished?
- Yes.

09:48.440 --> 09:49.480
Yes, we are.

09:49.480 --> 09:51.000
I'm putting an end to our little agreement.

09:51.000 --> 09:53.000
You're on your own, Franky.

10:14.860 --> 10:16.019
Bea.

10:16.519 --> 10:17.639
How'd it go?

10:20.240 --> 10:21.320
How's everything here?

10:21.320 --> 10:22.940
It's all good. It's good.

10:22.940 --> 10:26.519
'Cept the girls are still
testy about their privileges.

10:26.519 --> 10:28.519
Cindy Lou isn't happy.

10:30.399 --> 10:32.980
Cindy Lou's never happy.
What is it this time?

10:32.980 --> 10:34.980
You say we get time in the kitchen.

10:34.980 --> 10:36.980
