10:57.158 --> 10:59.158
Alright?

11:13.085 --> 11:15.114
- Or is it his tummy?
- Oh, hey!

11:15.114 --> 11:17.123
Do you wanna see my ultrasound?

11:17.123 --> 11:18.089
Yeah.

11:20.099 --> 11:22.831
- Ah.
- Isn't it gorgeous?

11:23.412 --> 11:25.643
- Yeah.
- I sent Nash a copy...

11:25.643 --> 11:27.352
He's gonna be so rapt!

11:27.352 --> 11:28.435
Hey, do you want a cuppa?

11:28.435 --> 11:30.444
Oh, no. I'm just gonna take a moment.

11:30.727 --> 11:32.574
Okay, well let me know
if you change your mind.

11:32.574 --> 11:34.583
Thanks. Oh, hey...

11:34.583 --> 11:36.592
Can you tell Franky I want to see her?

11:36.592 --> 11:37.257
And just...

11:37.257 --> 11:38.804
keep an eye on Cindy Lou and Tina, yeah?

11:38.804 --> 11:40.552
- Make sure there's no touble?
- Of course.

11:40.552 --> 11:41.755
Hey Bea?

11:41.755 --> 11:42.340
Yeah?

11:42.359 --> 11:44.228
How'd you go this morning?

11:44.750 --> 11:46.701
I got off!

11:50.337 --> 11:53.530
- Oh Doreen, I'm so excited!
- I know...

11:53.530 --> 11:55.539
I'm so excited, too!

12:06.330 --> 12:09.344
Bea Smith is a serious offender.

12:09.686 --> 12:13.664
And how we deal with her will be
highly scrutinized by the public.

12:13.664 --> 12:17.301
And a nervous government intent
on proving they are tough on crime.

12:17.301 --> 12:21.258
If she shows the slightest signs of
resistance, you will come down hard on her.

12:21.258 --> 12:23.268
- Understood?
- Yes, Governor.

12:23.268 --> 12:25.277
She is also highly manipulative.

12:25.619 --> 12:28.874
And the moment you feel sorry for her
is the moment you know she is using you.

12:28.874 --> 12:30.884
Isn't that right, Mr. Jackson?

12:30.884 --> 12:34.641
Mr. Jackson has just returned
from four months suspension...

12:34.641 --> 12:36.650
courtesy of Bea Smith.

12:37.956 --> 12:39.925
Welcome back, Mr. Jackson.

12:40.868 --> 12:42.437
- Governor.
- One more thing...

12:42.437 --> 12:46.214
The state government has instituted
a ban on smoking in all prisons,

12:46.214 --> 12:48.605
to be phased in over
the next twelve months.

12:48.605 --> 12:50.614
We will not be phasing it in.

12:51.556 --> 12:53.566
Wentworth starts today.

12:55.797 --> 12:56.942
Is there a problem?

12:56.942 --> 12:58.530
The women are already on edge.

12:58.530 --> 12:59.975
We've taken away their telly...

12:59.975 --> 13:01.443
Restricted their visits...

13:01.443 --> 13:03.452
- We take away their fags...
- This is government policy.

13:03.452 --> 13:05.461
Are you suggesting we ignore it?

13:05.461 --> 13:08.677
Smith's actions have thrown a
spotlight on everything you do.

13:08.677 --> 13:12.555
You can tell that to the women as
you confiscate their cigarettes.

13:12.555 --> 13:13.841
Yes, Governor.

13:13.841 --> 13:15.850
That'll be all, everyone. Thank you.

13:20.169 --> 13:22.579
Look, she's asking for
trouble is all I'm...

13:22.579 --> 13:23.867
- saying.
- Yeah, and it's our job

13:23.867 --> 13:25.876
to make sure that there isn't any.

13:27.302 --> 13:29.392
This is, uh, Bridget Westfall.

13:29.392 --> 13:30.557
Will Jackson.

13:30.557 --> 13:31.861
- G'day.
- Nice to meet you.

13:31.861 --> 13:34.415
Ms. Westfall is a forensic psychologist.

13:34.415 --> 13:35.238
She's...

13:35.238 --> 13:36.927
Joined the staff on a full-time basis,

13:36.927 --> 13:39.478
to run some anti-recidivism
programs with the women.

13:39.478 --> 13:41.488
Well, there's one you
won't have to worry about.

13:41.488 --> 13:43.777
Bea Smith. Life, no parole.

13:43.777 --> 13:45.183
When did this happen?

13:45.183 --> 13:46.229
This morning.

13:46.229 --> 13:48.800
We've just returned from
the Governor's briefing.

13:55.349 --> 13:56.696
Governor?

13:57.238 --> 13:59.330
May I have a word, please?

13:59.330 --> 14:01.377
How can I help you, Ms. Westnull?

14:01.377 --> 14:02.865
Westfall.

14:03.488 --> 14:05.999
Apparently there was a
staff briefing this morning.

14:05.999 --> 14:07.284
Why was I excluded?

14:07.284 --> 14:08.650
You are not my staff.

14:08.650 --> 14:10.099
You were a board appointment.

14:10.099 --> 14:11.365
Technically, yes.

14:11.365 --> 14:13.213
But if I'm to function as part of a team,

14:13.213 --> 14:14.359
- I really feel...
- Fine, as you wish.

14:14.359 --> 14:15.543
I will include you in the future.

14:15.543 --> 14:16.388
Anything else?

14:16.388 --> 14:17.934
I should meet with Smith today.

14:17.934 --> 14:19.542
If that's alright with you?

14:19.542 --> 14:21.552
I wasn't aware she'd
requested to see a psych.

14:21.552 --> 14:24.502
