14:26.575 --> 14:27.820
Of course...

14:27.820 --> 14:30.573
But I think you might
be overlooking something.

14:32.399 --> 14:33.626
What would that be?

14:33.626 --> 14:37.161
The board gave me pretty clear KPIs
on the prisoners' mental health.

14:37.161 --> 14:40.458
I hope you don't intend
to obstruct that brief.

14:42.849 --> 14:45.319
You can't have it both ways, Ms. Westfall.

14:45.319 --> 14:48.555
If you wish to be a member of my
team, you'll be reporting to me.

14:48.555 --> 14:49.941
Certainly.

14:50.384 --> 14:53.254
So, may I proceed?

14:54.945 --> 14:57.133
Be very cautious with Smith.

14:57.133 --> 14:58.963
She is a manipulator.

14:58.963 --> 15:00.309
Oh, don't worry, Governor.

15:00.309 --> 15:01.494
It's at the forefront of my mind.

15:01.494 --> 15:03.141
I'm trained to deal with all types.

15:03.141 --> 15:05.975
Even those who appear to
have their shit together.

15:10.936 --> 15:13.346
No, I don't wanna see
your fucking ultrasound.

15:13.346 --> 15:14.535
Where's Red?

15:17.327 --> 15:19.597
- You wanted a word?
- Yeah.

15:19.597 --> 15:20.862
Have a seat.

15:23.054 --> 15:25.324
- Everything good in the kitchen?
- All good.

15:25.324 --> 15:26.932
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

15:26.932 --> 15:29.121
Had a totally hilarious
tea towel fight with Booms.

15:29.121 --> 15:30.468
Gave her an epic bruise.

15:30.468 --> 15:33.984
- Still actually fucking hurts...
- Oh, suck it up, princess.

15:33.984 --> 15:36.655
Yeah, but Cindy Lou,
though. She's not very happy.

15:36.655 --> 15:37.539
Is she?

15:37.539 --> 15:39.549
Well, tell her she can come back.

15:39.891 --> 15:41.760
I promise not to use
the boning knife on her.

15:41.760 --> 15:43.769
Great, thanks.

15:44.069 --> 15:45.373
No problem.

15:45.919 --> 15:47.383
Anything else?

15:48.088 --> 15:49.392
No.

15:49.917 --> 15:50.981
Oh, yeah.

15:50.981 --> 15:52.549
You're still one short on the roster?

15:52.549 --> 15:54.275
Since Kimmie got paroled, yeah.

15:54.275 --> 15:56.568
Okay, well, maybe you can
give Maxine that detail.

15:56.568 --> 15:57.549
No.

15:57.549 --> 16:00.143
- We're all good, aren't we?
- Yeah, we're so fucking good.

16:00.143 --> 16:03.176
No, it's no hassle. I'm
sure she'd love to help out.

16:05.185 --> 16:07.639
Sure.

16:08.321 --> 16:09.145
Good.

16:09.484 --> 16:11.155
- And Franky?
- Hmm?

16:11.918 --> 16:16.135
It'd be a real problem for me if the drugs
coming in here are traced back to you.

16:16.135 --> 16:17.521
And why would they?

16:17.521 --> 16:19.530
I'm just saying.

16:20.337 --> 16:21.844
Mr. Jackson!

16:21.844 --> 16:22.828
You're back!

16:22.828 --> 16:24.837
Smith, you're wanted.

16:27.789 --> 16:29.137
Thanks.

16:32.189 --> 16:33.436
Hey, Mr. Jackson.

16:42.636 --> 16:45.110
So, how you been, Mr. Jackson?

16:47.341 --> 16:49.992
Didn't think they'd ever let you
escort me anywhere ever again.

16:57.566 --> 16:58.231
Come in.

16:58.231 --> 16:59.575
I didn't ask to see a psych.

16:59.575 --> 17:00.318
Well you should.

17:00.318 --> 17:03.193
You bloody need it.

17:06.186 --> 17:08.978
I'm Bridget Westfall,
forensic psychologist.

17:08.978 --> 17:10.125
Yeah, I know who you are.

17:10.125 --> 17:13.420
I asked to see you in the
wake of today's sentencing.

17:13.420 --> 17:15.430
How are you feeling?

