- I will not give in to these demands.

38:27.614 --> 38:29.024
- You listen to me,
- For God's sake.

38:29.024 --> 38:31.563
You will return to your unit...

38:31.964 --> 38:35.026
This is Derek Channing, general
manager of this facility.

38:35.026 --> 38:36.980
Officers in the isolation unit...

38:36.980 --> 38:38.471
Go to emergency channel.

38:38.471 --> 38:39.741
Yes, sir.

38:39.741 --> 38:40.870
Open the gates,

38:40.870 --> 38:42.360
