38:42.360 --> 38:43.044
and go.

38:43.044 --> 38:44.112
Do not make any move

38:44.112 --> 38:45.562
That puts Miss Bennet's life at risk.

38:45.562 --> 38:46.549
Am I clear?

38:46.549 --> 38:47.799
Yes, sir.

39:22.366 --> 39:23.896
Joan.

39:37.239 --> 39:38.259
Bea!

39:38.599 --> 39:39.378
Here.

39:39.378 --> 39:40.560
Bea!

39:40.560 --> 39:42.560
