39:44.143 --> 39:45.123
- Bea.
- Hi.

39:45.303 --> 39:47.443
We've got ourselves a friend.

39:47.904 --> 39:50.186
Well, lock her in here.

39:57.489 --> 39:58.950
Come on.

40:17.240 --> 40:19.281
