40:31.907 --> 40:36.069
Zero two, this is zero four.

40:36.069 --> 40:37.731
This is the Governor.

40:37.731 --> 40:40.431
The women want to speak to you.

40:40.431 --> 40:41.793
What do they want?

40:41.793 --> 40:44.174
They want to speak to you.

41:58.255 --> 42:00.256
- Mr. Jackson.
- Governor.

42:27.689 --> 42:33.835
Bea! Bea! Bea!

42:42.859 --> 42:44.259
Well?

42:45.941 --> 42:48.541
You haven't called in the squad.

42:49.822 --> 42:51.463
You don't know I haven't.

42:53.684 --> 42:57.367
And let the world know you've
lost control of this place?

42:57.827 --> 42:59.848
It was never gonna happen.

43:00.528 --> 43:02.988
I can put a stop to this now.

43:02.988 --> 43:04.710
Tell the women to back off,

43:04.710 --> 43:07.391
put down their weapons, send
them back to their units.

43:07.391 --> 43:09.653
Or, we can just stay here, hang out,

43:09.653 --> 43:11.574
until you're forced to call the squad.

43:11.574 --> 43:13.575
It's up to you.

43:18.458 --> 43:19.879
What do you want?

43:20.960 --> 43:24.080
No repercussions for
anyone involved here today.

43:25.302 --> 43:28.723
